Title: An Act Changing the Name of Imco Elementary School in the Municipality of Itogon, Province of Benguet, to Gaudencio E. Antonino, Sr. Memorial Elementary School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 722
An Act Changing the Name of Imco Elementary School in the Municipality of Itogon, Province of Benguet, to Gaudencio E. Antonino, Sr. Memorial Elementary School
Section 1. The name of the IMCO Elementary School in the Municipality of Itogon, Province of Benguet, is changed to Gaudencio E. Antonino Sr. Memorial Elementary School.1awphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: April 13, 1984
